            "english": "“Antidotal action is to put great effort into virtuous actions once you have committed a non-virtuous action.",
            "passage-xmlId": "UT22084-066-007-57",
            "creation_tool": "InterText",
            "volume": "66",
            "folio_xmlId": "UT4CZ5369-I1KG9192-0000/side/118"
        },
        {
